de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.analysis

Class ReadOnlyMeasurementResultAnalyserBlackboardView

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.analysis.ReadOnlyMeasurementResultAnalyserBlackboardView

  • public final class ReadOnlyMeasurementResultAnalyserBlackboardView
extends Object
    Read-only view of the Blackboard designed to be used by MeasurementResultAnalyser. It allows reading access for ResourceDemandMeasurementResults, BranchDecisionMeasurementResults and LoopRepetitionCountMeasurementResults .
